corruption scandal  - the concession of public works contracts in return for
kick-backs for illegal financing of political parties. Also allegedly
involved are two executives of construction companies, Mr Vincenzo
Lodigiani, head of his family company of the same name and Italy's second
largest constuction concern, and Mr Giorgio de Camillis, managing director
of Bonifica.
