FT  08 SEP 92 / The TUC At Blackpool: Lack of a national skills strategy
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By CATHERINE MILTON
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
TRAINING and Enterprise Councils, which administer government-funded
training programmes in England and Wales, are compromised by the lack of a
