to pursue sponsoring the league. The GM Vauxhall Conference yesterday signed
a one-year sponsorship agreement with the Health Education Authority for the
Bob Lord Challenge Trophy, which will become known as the Drinkwise Cup,
named after the authority's campaign to promote sensible consumption of
alcohol.
